DESCR = [ """A <AGE> <HEIGHT> <BUILD> person with <SKIN> skin. 
Their <EYE> eyes sit above a <NOSETYPE> nose and a <MOUTHTYPE> mouth. 
They have <HAIR> hair and <EYEBROW> eyebrows framing a <FACESHAPE> face with a <JAWSHAPE> jaw. 
A <DISTINCTMARK> stands out on their appearance, while their <BEARDTYPE> beard adds to their distinctive look.""" ]

